Corporate/M&A; lawyer, 5 to 6 years PQE, US firm, Singapore
Location:  Singapore
This is stand-out opportunity to join a world class law firm in a cutting edge and expanding corporate team in the Singapore market.
The workload will be a variety of high value cross-border M&A and private equity work, therefore strong experience is needed in this area from a top rated Corporate practice (Magic or Silver Circle UK, or top US/Australasian firm), where you will have been given significant responsibility on deals.
You will most likely be UK, Australia, or NZ qualified, have a confident personality, and have a strong academic record. In return a market leading salary and exposure to excellent work will be awaiting the successful candidate.
